# JD AI Text Summarizer

🔗 **Live App**: [https://jegan-06-jdsummary.streamlit.app](https://jegan-06-jdsummary.streamlit.app)

An AI-powered summarizer app that supports `.txt` and `.pdf` files.  
Built using BART from HuggingFace and Streamlit with a stylish custom UI.

## 🚀 Features:
- ✅ Abstractive Summarization using BART
- 📄 PDF and Text Upload
- 🎨 Custom Styled UI (Dark theme + Background)
- ⬇️ Download summary as `.txt` and `.pdf`

---

## 🧠 Built With:
- Python
- Streamlit
- HuggingFace Transformers
- PyMuPDF
- FPDF

